        "schema_version": "document-card-v1",
        "section_summaries": [
          {
            "section_id": "document-section:sha256:cf85b5b7503163332111c4fc79910a5dd391107bc65e11febcc67923a9573289",
            "summary": "概述TaskPool和Worker的作用，并说明本文将从实现特点和适用场景两方面进行对比。"
          },
          {
            "section_id": "document-section:sha256:ae910434e655a89120dbeee4c0b9b35b9776a04bf8759230311a56e1a9a28f65",
            "summary": "以表格形式对比TaskPool和Worker在内存模型、参数传递、方法调用、生命周期、任务管理功能等方面的实现差异。"
          },
          {
            "section_id": "document-section:sha256:8e8cfe38be3c91b20b666f1fa7e0a2c50d5eeb5fd81c7ac09411d245af906305",
            "summary": "总体说明TaskPool和Worker的适用倾向，指出TaskPool适合独立任务且自动管理，Worker适合需长时间运行或手动管理线程的场景。"
          },
          {
            "section_id": "document-section:sha256:b605cfb2ea785e648c0aa7415805666d36c16371fa1b914631a3617367a3b696",
            "summary": "列举建议使用Worker的具体场景，包括运行时间超过3分钟的任务和有强关联的同步任务。"
          },
          {
            "section_id": "document-section:sha256:a96fd0b8fbd5e2ae14de3e2d0a1d50f4fd26c6f900dae421e0ded05f74e12153",
            "summary": "列举建议使用TaskPool的具体场景，包括需设置优先级、频繁取消、大量或调度点分散的任务。"
          }
        ],
        "source_ref": {
          "anchor": "document",
